## Chat Operator Job Description
The Chat Operator is an online website consultant (an online website operator) who answers all questions from visitors and buyers in real-time. A specialist is to answer customer requests, tell customers about the website, and show where everything is located, just like any consultant in a real store.
## Main tasks of the Chat Operator
The main task of an online operatoris to answer calls or messages from a client immediately. Also, you will need to correspond with the client base, take customer queries and resolve issues on the basis of customer service standards, and provide fast, high-quality, and accurate information to customers.
## Chat Operator Requirements
* –êt least Intermediate level of English;
* Desire to work, study and develop;
* Fast typing;
* Sociability;
* To be a confident PC user.
Send us your contact details if you think you are suitable for this job.
## Ready to join?
To become part of our team, you need to record a short [video interview](/videointerview) in English and send it to us. After reviewing your resume, we will contact you for further collaboration.
